{"tid":544402,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"相戀是快樂的 然而邂逅卻是最大的不幸","createTime":"2018-01-29T12:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T13:03:30.000Z","uid":104130,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b75402066acd3b39c84e826c7040ccbe47b92dc6","tid":544402,"uid":104130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"好多時覺得真心鍾意一個人 就唔應該同佢一齊<br />\n因為永遠都係all or nothing <br />\n<br />\n又相遇到相知 每段回憶都係開心 正正係咁 分開先會特別難過<br />\n<br />\n拍過幾次拖 以為自己內心已經唔會再起咩波瀾 直到遇見妳 令我再有all in 嘅勇氣<br />\n<br />\n本以為今次可以扭轉命運 但最後都係衰係自己性格弱點手上 <br />\n<br />\n好多謝妳令我再一次有動力去改變自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n妳講得無錯 可能我好快就可以忘記妳 <br />\n<br />\n但的確係妳令我對愛情再次抱有信心 呢樣我永遠唔會忘記<br />\n<br />\n最後 雖然我話遇見妳可能係不幸 但我無後悔過<br />\n<br />\n希望妳都係<br />\n<br />\n（有感而發 多謝各位入咗嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"62946bf3875e98c841c1e6fe78a56b45d885a1b0","tid":544402,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"既然知道自己不足<br />\n就好好改變<br />\n不該白白失敗"},{"pid":"90a37faea477058815f47bb427574f7a2ac7c94a","tid":544402,"uid":104130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62946bf3875e98c841c1e6fe78a56b45d885a1b0","tid":544402,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"既然知道自己不足<br />\n就好好改變<br />\n不該白白失敗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:57:32.000Z","msg":"嗯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自虐嘅開心係估唔到自己依然會為分手而唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afd7fd229f98672e6591e6bb173d5beb7c37bd7","tid":544402,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a37faea477058815f47bb427574f7a2ac7c94a","tid":544402,"uid":104130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62946bf3875e98c841c1e6fe78a56b45d885a1b0","tid":544402,"uid":143307,"li